data.description: Amazingly large home on a full 5-acre lot. Welcome to the true countryside of warren county, Kentucky. This property features all the space one would need for a great affordable price comparable to today's general real estate pricing in the area for square footage, acreage, etc. Most may prefer what appears to be minor cosmetic repairs throughout and ground maintenance. Location, Location, Location within minutes from the Louisville Transit Park, Corvette Museum/Factory, Hot Rods Ball Park, Medical Center, downtown Bowling Green Area and much more! Exterior is wood siding. Must see property-call today for your tour!
